This is GUI that allows the user to manually segment food items in a set of test images (extension .PNM). The program was developed as part of a semester project for ECE 6930.

In order to implement active contours:
1. Select the On/Off option in the Contour menu after loading the image.
2. To implement a Shrink Contour, left click and drag around the object to initialize the contour points. Fora balloon contour, right click inside the object to intialize a set of contour points.
3. To start the contour, click 'R' for the shrink model and 'B' for the balloon model.

A report has been included going over the details and shortcomings.
